reviews.text: A great place to chill and relax on weekends.  Food quality is decent but the place is small so might need to wait for a bit before getting a seat there.

Located on a slope and it's a little trek from the MTR station on a sunny day with roasting temperature (32°C on the day I went). The Green All Day Breakfast includes a few things but the hash brown is real dry, the croissant has gone soft and there's only half a wild mushroom while the salad greens are warm. The flat white has very little to none microfoam, it simply tasted like a watered down milky coffee. I was rather disappointed at the quality of food for the price I paid.

Nice mood
price is bit high.
Food is good. Beer is quite good but not draft.
Good food and quite nice atmosphere
Love the ambience in this cafe. The beef and aubergine risotto was really delicious and coffee is great too. Would come back again

result.adr_address: 香港太平山東街53號
result.name: Oldish

reviews.text: 목재로 된 실내 분위기가 아주 아늑함. 아기자기하게 잘 인테리어해놓음. 식전에 고를수있는 머쉬룸스프는 고소하고 맛이 깊었으며, 연어가 올려진 에그베네딕트와 고기가 올라간 토마토파스타(이름이 정확히 무엇이었는지는 모르겠지만 메뉴추천해주심) 모두 무척 맛이 좋았음.

被環境吸引而至，氣氛好好，好適合傾計。
食物比想像好食，燒春雞好滑又多沖，配上蜜瓜青瓜一點點的酸汁清新開胃。
三文魚班尼迪都好食，但同燒春雞比就小左點驚喜啦！
懷舊，食物不錯， service都週到，全日早餐，GO
A stylish restaurant with good photo spots. 適合打卡及文青。

非常異國風情的店
英式風格的復古感
食物也很好吃
